data.title: 9 Field Commanders-RK-Platoon To Squad
data.meta_description: 9 Field Commanders-RK-Platoon to Squad - Free download as Word Doc (.doc / .docx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document lists the ranks, units, and dates of award for the Knight's Cross of the Iron Cross to various field commanders who led platoons and squads during World War 2. It includes over 150 recipients ranging from non-commissioned officers such as Oberfeldwebel to commissioned officers such as Leutnants. The listings provide brief details on the recipients' ranks, units, and the dates they were awarded Germany's highest military decoration.
